<L>__{exterior firing range day (early morning)}
<A>__{ on what's going to be a gorgeous day. burton, yawning, blowing into a steaming paper cup of coffee. collin, wide awake, moves alongside. collin is carrying a rifle. we are at a government firing range. collin squints into the morning sun. burton, putting down the coffee cup, picking up a pair of binoculars. burton and collin staring out a distant target is being raised. collin. he strokes the barrel of his high powered rifle.}
